OL,5, Four carers have been found guilty of  
OL,6, ill-treating patients at a secure      
OL,7, hospital, following a BBC Panorama     
OL,8, investigation.                         
OL,10,FNine former staff at Whorlton Hall,    
OL,11,Fnear Barnard Castle, County Durham, had
OL,12,Ffaced a total of 27 charges. Five of   
OL,13,Fthose on trial have been cleared.      
OL,15,FJurors heard vulnerable patients were  
OL,16,Fmocked and treated with "contempt".    
OL,18,FLawyers for the defendants argued their
OL,19,Fclients had been doing their best in   
OL,20,Fvery challenging circumstances.        
